text:
🦅🐦🦜This is one of the three Bird Hides located strategically along Diversity Trail at Tampines Eco Green.
🐦‍⬛Bird hide offers vistors close up view of the birds without intruding into their domains.
🍂🪶🦅The Bird Hides are make up of natural structures that blends in with the environment, allowing vistors to hide behind them to observe the birds in close proximity.
A hideout for se who wants to peek at the birds in the garden.
Good place for a nice evening walk
